PRACIS - A PRIVACY-PRESERVING AND AGGREGATABLE CYBERSECURITY INFORMATION SHARING MECHANISM
Prototype implementation
--------------------------

VERSION
--------

Version: 2016-05-01


AUTHORS
---------
Script: Lorena Gonzalez (lgmanzan at inf.uc3m.es), Jose Maria de Fuentes (jfuentes at inf.uc3m.es)

Paper: Jose Maria de Fuentes (jfuentes at inf.uc3m.es), Lorena Gonzalez (lgmanzan at inf.uc3m.es), Juan M. Estevez-Tapiador (jestevez at inf.uc3m.es), Pedro Peris (pperis at inf.uc3m.es)

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
---------------------------

In order to run these scripts the following elements are prerequisites:
* Python-STIX (https://github.com/STIXProject/python-stix)
* Charm-crypto (http://charm-crypto.com/)
* LibFTE (https://libfte.org/)

USAGE
------

PRACIS_EncryptDecryptTest.py : This script prepares a STIX packet and applies Homomorphic encryption and Format-Preserving encryption over different fields, as described in the paper. It shows the time taken in these operations.

No parameters are needed.

PRACIS_AggregationTest.py : This script measures the time taken to perform the aggregation of STIX packets, as described in the paper.

No parameters are needed. 


